{"tid":1756811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每次勇武打仗 都有至少兩萬人坐喺屋企睇直播","createTime":"2019-11-26T08:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T08:52:38.000Z","uid":183771,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d077bc8307ce090b005b10b916cb8346c763fb","tid":1756811,"uid":183771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:04:49.000Z","msg":"次次睇蘋果直播都有成四萬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當有一半喺五毛或者藍屍 不過藍屍應該通常睇CCTVB<br />\n都有兩萬人喺冷氣軍師 <br />\n你可以話自己喺哨兵或者幫手Cap圖搵被捕人士朋友屋企人 <br />\n但一定唔喺勇武<br />\n依家勇武要休息 你班契弟想睇人打仗就叫人出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早已經應承抗爭喺長時間<br />\n怕埸運動會降溫咪攪和理非活動<br />\n你班睇直播嘅冷氣軍師（懶得幫手share圖嗰班）<br />\n冇撚資格對勇武指手畫腳 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔該你哋諗下自己有咩可以貢獻到 </span> <br />\n有一半人幫手喺Tg做資料整合 分分鐘已經可以避免多一位手足被失蹤<br />\n<br />\n利申：和理非 不割蓆 日日J勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f81893a64c42b4dca00bdba3984e671739a932","tid":1756811,"uid":274538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:05:52.000Z","msg":"呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/goHOmop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgoHOmop.jpg&h=ed61e258&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff03b3d48f68aa17037e9cd4b86aedbd26597098","tid":1756811,"uid":183771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4153826dbb27993de140297a6ff6f972f2efca","tid":1756811,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:08:32.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n冷氣軍師通常係散水撚同中計撚同民意撚<br />\n只會叫你走同乜都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b38cce3a91c5feee8ff6818d8559494346df54e","tid":1756811,"uid":1477,"like":0,"d